OL,3,CUnited States seeking an armed
OL,4,Cuprising inside Iran
OL,6,FThe United States and Israel are
OL,7,Fseeking to foment an armed uprising
OL,8,Finside Iran using an armed Kurdish
OL,9,Ffighting force, which has been built
OL,10,Fup since the twelve-day war in 2025.
OL,12,FITV News understands that since last
OL,13,Fyear, weapons have been smuggled into
OL,14,FWestern Iran to arm thousands of
OL,15,FKurdish volunteers. They are expected
OL,16,Fto begin a ground operation within
OL,17,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
