OL,3,CUnited States seeking an armed
OL,4,Cuprising inside Iran
OL,6,FIn recent days, American and Israeli
OL,7,Fstrikes have repeatedly struck
OL,8,Fsecurity targets in the West of the
OL,9,Fcountry to degrade their capabilities
OL,10,Fand give the best chance for the
OL,11,Fground rebellion.
OL,13,FWe have been told by Kurdish sources
OL,14,Fthat American and Israeli forces have
OL,15,Fbeen asked to provide air cover when
OL,16,Fany such ground operation begins. Our
OL,17,Fsources do not know if that request
OL,18,Fhas been approved.
OL,20,FIn recent days Iran has increased its
OL,21,Fbombing of Kurdish rebel areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
