OL,3,CUnited States seeking an armed
OL,4,Cuprising inside Iran
OL,6,FThis weekend, President Trump has
OL,7,Fspoken to Iranian and Iraqi Kurdish
OL,8,Fleaders based in Northern Iraq.
OL,10,FIt is likely those conversations
OL,11,Fraised the issue of a ground
OL,12,Frebellion, no one involved in the
OL,13,Fcalls have spoken about them.
OL,15,FKaroline Leavitt, the White House
OL,16,Fpress secretary confirmed the
OL,17,FPresident had spoken many regional
OL,18,Fpartners. US officials told the Wall
OL,19,FStreet Journal that President Trump
OL,20,Fwas considering requests to provide
OL,21,Fsupport.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
