OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772625779
OL,3,CUnited States seeking an armed
OL,4,Cuprising inside Iran
OL,6,FAt the weekend he also shared a
OL,7,FWashington Post opinion article which
OL,8,Fsuggested that there is no need for US
OL,9,Fforces to mount a ground operation as
OL,10,Fthe Iranian people will be "the boots
OL,11,Fon the ground".
OL,13,FA successful uprising may well be
OL,14,Fwishful thinking however, given how
OL,15,FIran has fortified its military
OL,16,Fpresence around the Kurdish areas and
OL,17,Fwould crack down hard on any attempt
OL,18,Fto rebel.
