OL,3,CUnited States seeking an armed
OL,4,Cuprising inside Iran
OL,6,FThere are around ten million Kurds
OL,7,Fwithin Iran, and thousands have passed
OL,8,Fthrough training in the mountains over
OL,9,Fmany years.
OL,11,FWhilst there may be a greater
OL,12,Fwillingness to support from Iranian
OL,13,FKurdish leaders, it is likely there
OL,14,Fwill be huge caution from Iraqi
OL,15,FKurdish leaders given the Iranian
OL,16,Fresponse on other nations which have
OL,17,Fsupported the war so far.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
