OL,3,CUnited States seeking an armed
OL,4,Cuprising inside Iran
OL,6,FFurthermore, the Kurds have been used
OL,7,Fby the United States in the past and
OL,8,Fthen abandoned. The Kurds were
OL,9,Fcritical to the fight against ISIS
OL,10,Fonly to find the USA walked away from
OL,11,Fthe support they had expected once
OL,12,Fthat war was won.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
